data.description: Check out this 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom in Grande Champion! On the first floor you'll find an office or sitting room, living room and dining room. The open concept gives ample room for hosting. In the kitchen, you'll find a stove top and granite countertops. The double wall oven and smart refrigerator is sure to catch your eye. Lastly, you'll find a powder room just before you go upstairs. Upstairs features a nice large open loft that can have many versatile uses. Here, you'll be able to access all three bedrooms branching off. Also located upstairs is the laundry room with storage. A bathroom is easily accessible down the same hall as bedrooms 2-3. In the master bedroom you'll notice plenty of room for furniture with a large bathroom with a tub, shower and a walkin closet. Outside you'll find a nice covered patio and a fenced yard for the pups to run. The home is wired with a security system that you can easily continue service with. Lastly, the two car garage will allow you to tuck your vehicles away or give you even more storage!
